Assurant Inc. (AIZ) , the insurer of
foreclosed properties, appointed Robert W. Stein to the board of
directors.  Stein, 62, will join Oct. 1 after retiring from Ernst &
Young where he is a global managing partner of actuarial
services, the New York-based insurer said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
